-This application uses the built-in in-memory HSQLDB that comes with every
Grails app.

-You may need to execute `grails upgrade` prior to running the app or running
the tests.

-One-to-many relationships -- Check out the domain
classes in grails-app/domain. In there you'll find the Knight and Sword
domain classes. Knights have many swords, and swords belong to knights.
